{"tid":373010,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一個魚拉突 咁既分組真係得啖笑","createTime":"2017-08-24T16:55:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T17:34:29.000Z","uid":86805,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"574f1d73833959cb17905cc196dbc0362af420f9","tid":373010,"uid":86805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T16:55:58.000Z","msg":"作為一個魚拉突 咁既分組真係得啖笑<br />\n<br />\n講真咁同直接宣佈曼首名有咩分別。<br />\n<br />\n令我地班魚拉突 totally no mood to 捱夜睇波 嗱,我又分析下 首先賓咩加,唔好玩啦 葡萄牙野，6分穩陣<br />\n<br />\n巴素利,,如果係巴狗就有可觀性(順便可以報上次ga仇)(不過算啦,入到決賽又會見到面) 我真係冇睇過依隊野..曼半力夠WIN,又6分<br />\n<br />\n最後一隊,我連名都唔記得 我地出青年軍練下is ok,又6分<br />\n<br />\n加上我地4大尖刀 普巴,連加特,盧卡古,伊巴 加上關鍵王朗尼.. 根本場場大炒,,,,<br />\n<br />\n18分就一定..係睇下破唔破到得失球.咁一面倒ga比賽,我冇興趣,大家16強見<br />\n<br />\nP.S.比d咁ga對手魚拉突..is侮辱..哈"},{"pid":"591fd843f2cb32993dcd7066b4f280bdde6320ec","tid":373010,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T16:57:23.000Z","msg":"朗尼??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6ec970f1bed274ecf6c8b51bcc1e0b86a7a0b4","tid":373010,"uid":74081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T16:59:35.000Z","msg":"聽人講朗尼loan咗返曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d63f2eac83e5297100e5e1c3fde54a153bf0ee7","tid":373010,"uid":37566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:01:03.000Z","msg":"痴線一模一樣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"526139b201927efdcab87ac2bab8acd6e89fe3a1","tid":373010,"uid":111425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:02:05.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 換球員名就又一篇新潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41a3367ac0ae0dab74cbf88551fa382f0db23d8","tid":373010,"uid":118562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:02:17.000Z","msg":"真係倒模都無咁似<img src=\"/a